        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(4 comments)\n\nlooks nice, and shows good understanding of the mechanism. added my few small suggestions. \n\nin addition please note that this change looks like it is expected to give the following feature: \nafter creation and ticking the box - a pause on pause point icon should be visible on screen.\nalso if user adds a pause point - this should be visible in the vfmodule edit screen.\n\nthis behavior and similar should be verified, presumably in a cypress test. (can be a subsequent commit.)",
